                                   Introduction
                                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
          This manual assumes you are familiar with the RISC OS desktop. You
          may want to read the Welcome Guide and the User Guide#url
          http://acorn.riscos.com/riscos3/37/37DiscImage/Manuals/Manual/BOOKB/
          BOOK_3.HTM> that come with your RISC OS system.
          You may also want to read this introduction to RISC OS.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Lender is a small 'database' which will keep a list of all the things
    people borrow from you thus allowing you to keep track of these things.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                      Previous
                                                                          Next
    ==========================================================================

                                   Installation
                                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
      è   Download the program.
      è   The program is compressed into a Zip archive. Decompress it using
          e.g. SparkFS or Sparkplug#URL
          http://pilling.users.netlink.co.uk/free.html>.
      è   Copy the decompressed application, and any other files in the
          archive, to a place on your harddisc.
      è   That is it - you have installed Lender.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                      Previous
                                                                          Next
    ==========================================================================

                                     Starting
                                     ~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
          Use the interactive help to get help on specific icons and
          menuitems.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Viewing
        è    Click SELECT on the iconbar icon to view the main window which
             displays a list of the things borrowed from you.

    Add an item

                                                                        Page 1

             è    SELECT click on on this button to open the Add item window.
             è    Enter the data end press RETURN or click on OK.

    Edit an entry

             è    Doubleclick on the entry you want to edit - this will open
                  the edit window.
             è    Make the changes and click OK.

    Delete an Item

             è    SELECT the item(s) you want to delete.
             è    SELECT click on the button.

    (De-)Select all

         Click SELECT to select all items in the list. Click ADJUST to
         deselect all items in the list.

    Find

         Click SELECT to open find window. Click ADJUST to repeat previous
         search.
         All items in the list which match the search expression will be
         selected. 

    Sorting

         Click SELECT to perform a sort. Click ADJUST to repeat the previos
         sort.


    Saving
    Lender saves all the data whenever anything is changed.
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
