                                    Shortcuts
                                    ~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
        F1   Shows the manual.
    control  F1   Runs the interactive help.
    control  W    Opens the webpage.

        F4   Opens the Search window.
    shift    F4   Repeats the previous search.

    control  N    Opens the Add item window.
    control  E    Opens the Edit item window.
    control  X    Deletes the selected item(s).
    control  S    Sorts the list.

    control  A    Selects all items in the list.
    control  Z    Removes the selection.

    control  Q    Quits.
